<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Hello Kitty Page</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8b9ce, #f5d6c7, #fcd2a1);
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 700px;
        max-height: 90vh;
        background: #ffffffdd;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        text-align: center;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
        overflow-y: auto;
        border: 3px solid #f7a6b3;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #ed164f;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #f07bb6;
        margin-top: 0;
      }

      p {
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 8px 0;
        color: #444;
      }

      .tagline {
        font-style: italic;
        color: #f06292;
      }

      .badges {
        margin: 15px 0;
      }

      .badge {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        margin: 4px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #ffe7f1;
        color: #d81b60;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
      }

      .photo {
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .photo img {
        max-height: 40vh;
        width: auto;
        border-radius: 15px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        border: 4px solid #f8b9ce;
      }

      .photo img:hover {
        transform: scale(1.05);
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      }

      .footer {
        margin-top: 15px;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: #777;
      }

      a {
        color: #ed164f;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      a:hover {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }

      @media (max-width: 600px) {
        .container {
          padding: 16px;
          margin: 10px;
        }
        .photo img {
          max-height: 30vh;
          max-width: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div>
        <h1>Hello Kitty Corner</h1>
        <h2 class="tagline">Cute, cozy, and a little bit pink ✨</h2>

        <p>
          Welcome to your tiny Hello Kitty–themed page! You can customize this
          however you like using HTML or EJS.
        </p>
        <p>
          Try adding your favorite quotes, fun facts, or even a mini blog about why
          you love Hello Kitty. Replace text, colors, and the image below to make
          it your own.
        </p>

        <div class="badges">
          <span class="badge">♡ kawaii vibes</span>
          <span class="badge">♡ pastel colors</span>
          <span class="badge">♡ Sanrio fan</span>
        </div>

        <p>
          This file could be named
          <strong><%= name %>.ejs</strong>
          and placed inside your <strong>views</strong> folder in an Express app.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="photo">
        <!-- Replace /hello-kitty.png with your actual image path -->
        <img src="/hello-kitty.png" alt="Hello Kitty" />
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        Made with ♥ in EJS —
        <a href="https://ejs.co/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">learn more about EJS</a>.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
